<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two joining fragments from the lower left corner of a large <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="base">statue base</rs> with flat moulding (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.05</measure>) below (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height" precision="circa">0.80</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.32</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.60</measure>).</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.075-0.08</measure></p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date exact="none" cert="low">III-IV</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>

<div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="1"/>  <w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w>  <w lemma="δῆμος">Δῆμ<supplied reason="lost">ος <space extent="3"/></supplied></w>  <lb n="2"/><w lemma="ὁ">τὴν</w>  <w lemma="βουλή">Βουλ<supplied reason="lost">ὴν</supplied></w>  </ab>
</div>

<div type="history" n="text-constituted-from">
<head>Text Constituted From</head>
<p>Transcription (Reynolds)</p>
</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The People (set up a statue of) the Council.</p>
</div>

<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p> The Council honoured the Demos in a pair to this (<xref type="inscription" n="817" href="020111">2.111</xref>). The lettering might suggest a late antique date; but if these texts were inscribed by the sculptors, and not by professional letterers the argument is not strong.</p><p>For another base for an image of the Council, see <xref type="inscription" n="863" href="080503">8.503</xref>.</p>
</div>

<div type="history" n="locations">
<head>Locations</head>
<p> <rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">Bouleuterion/Odeon</rs> Parodos area, 1966.2</rs> <rs type="origLocation">Unknown</rs> <rs type="lastLocation">Right fragment lying north of Odeon (2000)</rs>.</p>
</div>





